{"tid":1888203,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【factcheck假新聞】【連環大炒車】邊撚度有27個專家響lancet聯署譴責陰謀論？","createTime":"2020-02-20T05:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T05:56:25.000Z","uid":138409,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b90246087fc7a3983aa9a438b6fb7f2d8768739f","tid":1888203,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:07:06.000Z","msg":"【轉自fb friend】<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Tl;dr</span></span><br />\n麻煩各位記者朋友<br />\n下次cite paper前<br />\n記得睇左篇paper講乜先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n呢兩日唔少新聞都話「周三2月19日，27個公共衛生專家聯署對新冠病毒並非自然源起的陰謀論予以強烈譴責。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3XvaB5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3XvaB5.png&h=8544f96d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Osz5JW6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOsz5JW6.png&h=7379806c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49n7cQr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49n7cQr.png&h=6b0b0d8c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qd3Y3W7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQd3Y3W7.png&h=26d66e50&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qNCSoW7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqNCSoW7.png&h=075e84ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例如<br />\n健康資訊網站「<span style=\"color: gold;\">醫。思維</span>」之文章<br />\n<a href=\"https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/48604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedicalinspire.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F48604&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=65167ee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/48604</a><br />\n聲稱港大教授潘烈文（Poon Lit Man）有份聯署，並引用lancet呢篇名為&ldquo;Tracking online heroisation and blame in epidemics&rdquo;論文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lanpub/article/PIIS2468-2667(20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flanpub%2Farticle%2FPIIS2468-2667%2820&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=b5747a1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lanpub/article/PIIS2468-2667(20</a>)30033-5/fulltext#coronavirus-linkback-header<br />\n<br />\n至於最早相關消息來自HK01<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/436836/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%88%BA%E9%87%9D-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%87%E6%BA%90%E8%AA%BF%E5%8B%95%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F436836%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2588%25BA%25E9%2587%259D-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25BA%2590%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%258B%2595%25E9%2580%259F%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%258F%258A&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=25cf0f5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/436836/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%88%BA%E9%87%9D-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%87%E6%BA%90%E8%AA%BF%E5%8B%95%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%8A</a><br />\n但係並唔係引用&ldquo;Tracking online heroisation and blame in epidemics&rdquo;，而係引用lancet呢篇名為&ldquo;Challenges of coronavirus disease 2019&rdquo;嘅論文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thelancet.com/action/showPdf?pii=S1473-3099%2820%2930072-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Faction%2FshowPdf%3Fpii%3DS1473-3099%252820%252930072-4&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=d6f99e4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thelancet.com/action/showPdf?pii=S1473-3099%2820%2930072-4</a><br />\n<br />\n問題就來了<br />\n1.<br />\n&rdquo;Tracking online heroisation and blame in epidemics&ldquo;呢篇論文<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">作者只有5人</span></span>，完全唔係啲乜嘢「來自8個國家和地區的27名知名公共衞生專家」聯署<br />\n更加<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">完全無「對新冠病毒並非自然源起的陰謀論予以強烈譴責」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有關陰謀論（conspiracy）嘅字眼只係出現2次，都係叫政府密切留意網上謠言。<span style=\"color: gold;\">甚至篇文仲提醒政府透明度嘅重要性，指唔單止要留意陰謀論，亦都要留意衛生機構自己有無做好溝通</span><br />\n// Searching for someone to blame is part of the process of making sense of any disaster, akin to the phenomenon of moral panic. Conspiracy theories and misinformation are already circulating in traditional and social media about COVID-19. Thus, it is important to track the evolving dynamics of blame in real time, both to correct inaccurate information and to respond to online scapegoating.//<br />\n// Qualitative analysis can also identify issues in authorities' handling of crises, which crystallise around transparency. <span style=\"color: gold;\">For instance, discussions can coalesce not only around conspiracy theories but also around real uncertainties and blind spots in health authorities' communications.</span>//<br />\n<br />\n2.我上lancet嘅網站搜尋2月19日publish嘅paper<br />\n亦都唔見類似嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n至於HK01嘅報導就無咩問題嘅，基本上都係譯返篇paper<br />\n但亦都係<span style=\"color: gold;\">完全無提及乜嘢「來自8個國家和地區的27名知名公共衞生專家聯署對新冠病毒並非自然源起的陰謀論予以強烈譴責」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結論：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係久違嘅連環炒車啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n備註：<br />\n用google新聞搜尋關鍵字「潘烈文」，類似報導有：<br />\n中時電子報<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200219004924-260408?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200219004924-260408%3Fchdtv&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=651706e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200219004924-260408?chdtv</a><br />\n東網：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200219/bkn-20200219183205929-0219_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200219%2Fbkn-20200219183205929-0219_00912_001.html&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=269df439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200219/bkn-20200219183205929-0219_00912_001.html</a><br />\n香港電台<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509555-20200219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509555-20200219.htm&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=8dc51afc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509555-20200219.htm&h=c66e94c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509555-20200219.htm</a><br />\n蘋果日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200219/HNF6WLDP3HFV53WSUPZSDR5SV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200219%2FHNF6WLDP3HFV53WSUPZSDR5SV4%2F&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=a250d98f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200219%2FHNF6WLDP3HFV53WSUPZSDR5SV4%2F&h=75cf0f00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200219/HNF6WLDP3HFV53WSUPZSDR5SV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n但係佢哋好多都無cite source，都係互相抄襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">類似連環炒車情況之前都試過㗎</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n孟加拉難民強暴女高中生 法國法院以文化不同判無罪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/952186/page/9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/952186/page/9</a><br />\n&rarr; factcheck <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/952548/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/952548/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n傳播途徑la manch libre&rarr; voice of europe&rarr; wnd&rarr; 自由時報--&gt; 連登<br />\n<br />\n人類總是犯重複錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f80922d0a6f805ffd8244ed36567cc34f6667ee","tid":1888203,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"511d82582b51fcd568ad1fd910c64544ecf1d6f5","tid":1888203,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"英文都炒車"},{"pid":"943439d43f681a315205b265bbe049ddacc568e2","tid":1888203,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c0e3b693e29608ea1c78b642c60f6424ddeefee8","tid":1888203,"uid":138388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8df1f458be929bad36ca1a87f6473b101d35b920","tid":1888203,"uid":112622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76f3e75e1bf6a292610307b48e1221337288b54c","tid":1888203,"uid":315523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:16:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1f6b24584c041ed1d39475c523e176d3045f4300","tid":1888203,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"908089a53538f7a5dc8e01db6438bd657f00cb5b","tid":1888203,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"講緊依篇呀嘛<br />\n<a h